{"tid":88081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美圖秀秀拎Android機大量私隱資訊  被發現連結至支那伺服器","createTime":"2017-01-20T10:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T03:18:43.000Z","uid":1886,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19aab7741bdde0b8a4ee126962cc85954eb7706d","tid":88081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T10:43:18.000Z","msg":"美圖秀秀拎Android機大量私隱資訊　被發現連結至支那伺服器<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2017/01/photo-app-meitu-is-sending-imei-mac-address-data/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2017%2F01%2Fphoto-app-meitu-is-sending-imei-mac-address-data%2F&d=w7SRCe7k2aCBnNsguPYfLJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=de7c6c14\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2017/01/photo-app-meitu-is-sending-imei-mac-address-data/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">哈哈哈哈</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問吓前幾日用過呢個app嘅連登仔點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7e6340f8ed3656d0cc732ec547343a9b83086b","tid":88081,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T10:45:19.000Z","msg":"作為香港人，或許已經對這些報道不奇怪，但香港人仍然唔知死，近來有不少人照用大陸的美圖秀秀。外國有人發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">美圖秀秀不正常地傳送IMEI、MAC（即裝置獨有的位址）、機型號、解像度、Android OS版本等，網民@FourOctets更發現，使用美圖秀秀時會有正常地與大陸IP連接</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nAndroidPolice稱他們無法100%證實美圖秀秀是否與大陸IP連接，但確認<span style=\"color: red;\">美圖秀秀的確存取太多權限</span>。而網民@rekrom12亦確認當中